'''Amber''' was a smuggler in the organization of [[Mazzic]]. She was the pilot of the ''[[Skyclaw]]''.<ref name="The Last Command">[[The Last Command]]</ref>

In 9 ABY, she escorted Mazzic on the ''[[Distant Rainbow]]'', along with [[Griv]], to a smugglers' meeting organized by [[Talon Karrde]] on the planet [[Hijarna]]. During the meeting, after [[Niles Ferrier]]'s treachery was revealed, Mazzic signaled her and Griv to take down [[The Gunship|the ship thief's Corellian Gunship]] as he tried to escape the planet, which they did.<ref name="The Last Command" />

